detail.name: Piercing Sword of Light
detail.effect: [Activate Main] If your Leader is <Vegito>, look at 3 cards from the top of your deck, reveal up to 1 card with a cost of 4 or less and 《Saiyan》 in its special traits and add it to your hand. Place the rest into its owner's Drop.

detail.name: 貫く光の剣
detail.effect: 【起動 メイン】自分のリーダーが「ベジット」の場合、自分のデッキの上から3枚を見て、コスト4以下の特徴《サイヤ人》を持つカード1枚までを公開し、手札に加える。残りをドロップに置く。
